					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5735251#post-3770250</guid>
				<title>Author post · SCP-3211: There is No Canon</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5735251/scp-3211#post-3770250</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 15 Apr 2018 22:31:33 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Croquembouche</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2893766</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>One chance and six minutes between you and the abyss of ignorance.</p> <p>Big thanks to the following:</p> <ul> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mayd" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1422059&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607331972" alt="MayD" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1422059)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mayd" >MayD</a></span> for advice</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ayers" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1856789&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607331972" alt="Ayers" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1856789)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ayers" >Ayers</a></span> for technical help regarding CSS</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607331972" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" >Captain Kirby</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zzuxon" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1496981&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607331972" alt="Zzuxon" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1496981)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zzuxon" >Zzuxon</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ayers" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1856789&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607331972" alt="Ayers" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1856789)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ayers" >Ayers</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=637830&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607331972" alt="SoullessSingularity" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=637830)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" >SoullessSingularity</a></span> for criticism, support and helpful tips</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/flagsam" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3696091&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607331972" alt="flagsam" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3696091)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/flagsam" >flagsam</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmartens" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4618927&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607331972" alt="DrMartens" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4618927)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmartens" >DrMartens</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/inkmouth" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5313894&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607331972" alt="Inkmouth" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5313894)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/inkmouth" >Inkmouth</a></span> for inspiration</li> </ul> <p>This one draws heavily from 3125 in formatting, so an indirect thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/qntm" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=571081&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607331972" alt="qntm" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=571081)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/qntm" >qntm</a></span>, I guess</p> <p>Did I forget anyone? My apologies - please send me a very angry PM and I'll add you to the list.</p> <p>I hope you enjoy.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Image&nbsp;credits</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>In the interest of spoilers, many of the following are <strong>decoys</strong>. They are all CC0, CC-BY, CC-SA, CC-BY-SA or public domain.</p> <p>Creative Commons:</p> <ul> <li>Bus <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Plymouth_Hoe_Road_-_Western_National_2019_(824KDV).jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Plymouth_Hoe_Road_-_Western_National_2019_(824KDV).jpg</a></li> <li>Netball player <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Poznarova.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Poznarova.jpg</a></li> <li>Dead pigeon <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Dead_pigeon_IMG_1282.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Dead_pigeon_IMG_1282.jpg</a></li> <li>Butterfly <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Colias_staudingeri_staudingeri_female_Paralectotype_04_dorsal_side_ZISP.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Colias_staudingeri_staudingeri_female_Paralectotype_04_dorsal_side_ZISP.jpg</a></li> <li>&quot;No image available&quot; is from <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-231">SCP-231</a> so credit to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drclef" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=213153&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607331972" alt="DrClef" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=213153)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drclef" >DrClef</a></span></li> <li>Gold coin <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/47445767@N05/34624018555">https://www.flickr.com/photos/47445767@N05/34624018555</a></li> <li>Matchbox <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/evaekeblad/8314435089/">https://www.flickr.com/photos/evaekeblad/8314435089/</a></li> <li>Toaster <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Toaster1.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Toaster1.jpg</a></li> <li>Gloves <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/el_cajon_yacht_club/28096590309">https://www.flickr.com/photos/el_cajon_yacht_club/28096590309</a></li> <li>Putty <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/85659491@N00/458381711">https://www.flickr.com/photos/85659491@N00/458381711</a></li> <li>Milk1 <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Dairy_Crest_Semi_Skimmed_Milk_Bottle.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Dairy_Crest_Semi_Skimmed_Milk_Bottle.jpg</a></li> <li>Milk2 <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Milk_glass.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Milk_glass.jpg</a></li> <li>Milk3 <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Muesli.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Muesli.jpg</a></li> <li>Building <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:MPD_Exterior.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:MPD_Exterior.jpg</a></li> </ul> <p>Public Domain:</p> <ul> <li>BSicon <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:BSicon_eKRZr%2Br.svg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:BSicon_eKRZr%2Br.svg</a></li> <li>Red cube <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Uniform_polyhedron-43-t0.png">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Uniform_polyhedron-43-t0.png</a></li> <li>State of Louisiana <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Louisiana_975.svg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Louisiana_975.svg</a></li> <li>Chocolates <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:ChocolateBox.JPG">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:ChocolateBox.JPG</a></li> <li>Milk4 <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Johannes_Vermeer_-_Het_melkmeisje_-_Google_Art_Project_(fragment).jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Johannes_Vermeer_-_Het_melkmeisje_-_Google_Art_Project_(fragment).jpg</a></li> <li>Milk5 <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/fdaphotos/32404676395">https://www.flickr.com/photos/fdaphotos/32404676395</a></li> <li>Boats <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:War_Office_Second_World_War_Official_Collection_H17361.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:War_Office_Second_World_War_Official_Collection_H17361.jpg</a></li> <li>Map <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Guide_to_the_great_Coeur_d%27Alene_gold_field_(NBY_17320).jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Guide_to_the_great_Coeur_d%27Alene_gold_field_(NBY_17320).jpg</a></li> </ul> <p>Created by me (CC0):</p> <ul> <li>&quot;The Fishery&quot;</li> <li>puce</li> <li>A bag of cashews</li> <li>Milk6, Milk7, Milk8</li> <li>Dr Noppler</li> <li>Dr Noppler's Cutlery</li> <li>&quot;The Beast&quot;</li> <li>The &quot;infohazard warning&quot; thing on the starting page</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Major&nbsp;spoilers</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <h3><span>Major spoilers below, do not read if you've not already read SCP-3211</span></h3> <p>If you've spoken to someone else who's read this then you'll have noticed that there are multiple versions of this document. You only get to read one, but someone else might have been given a different one to read. It is selected randomly, and represents the fact that your in-universe &quot;researcher&quot; has generated a false memory, as detailed in the document. The first version of the document that you read represents this false memory.</p> <p>Of course, it's not fair to only let you read it once - what if you prefer to read slowly? - so here's a few tips for you.</p> <hr /> <p>If you want to see the original version again, on the starting page click &quot;AUTHORISATION&quot; at the bottom, then click the button &quot;Ignore seen&quot; that appears, then click &quot;Proceed&quot;</p> <p>(to get to the starting page, just refresh the page)</p> <p>If you want to make the document completely forget you've read it, click &quot;Reset&quot;</p> <p>If you want to manually select a new version of the SCP to read, click &quot;Reset&quot; then one of the numbers 0 - 3.</p> <p>To stop the timer, click &quot;Stop timer&quot; while the timer is running</p> <p>To get a running log of what the SCP is doing, open up the JavaScript console (Ctrl+Shift+I on Chrome)</p> </div> </div> </div> <h2><span>Fast reader?</span></h2> <p>If you're done reading but the timer is still running, to skip ahead to the final version click the word &quot;READ&quot; in the note above the timer. This will set the timer to 5 seconds</p> <p><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/cone">More stuff by me</a></p> 
